        <!-- ================= NOTE ================= -->
        <mxCell id="note" value="How connectivity stays private&#10;• EventBridge, Step Functions, Athena, Glue, S3 &amp; KMS are regional AWS services — not in the VPC.&#10;• VPC compute reaches them via Gateway (S3) &amp; Interface / PrivateLink endpoints — Athena, Glue, ECR, Logs, KMS/STS stay off the NAT / public path.&#10;• data.gov.sg is reached outbound-only through NAT Gateways (one per AZ)." style="rounded=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=6;fillColor=#F5F5F5;strokeColor=#B0B0B0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=8;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
